<div class="container">
  <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
    <h1>Welcome, <%=@user.name%> </h1> 
    
    <% if @user.group == nil%>  
    
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Go ahead and create your group</h2>
        <form action="/groups" method="Post">
          <label for="name"><strong>Name: </strong> 
          <br>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Your group's name here"></label>
          <br>
          <label for="bio"><strong>Bio:</strong>
          <br>
          <textarea type="text" id="bio" name="bio" placeholder="Tell us about your group please." rows="10" cols="50"></textarea></label>
          <br>
          <button type="submit" value="submit"><strong>Submit!<strong></button>
        </form>
      </div>
        
    <%else%>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>Wait just a minute...</h2>
        <p> I do apologize but you cannot create a group while you are in a group. Creators must be apart of their group (or at least when they first start it). Since you can only be a member of one group at a time. You would need to leave your current group first.</p>
        <h3>Leave Group?</h3>
        <p>To leave your group please visit their page and click the "Leave" button on the groups page. The group you are currently apart of is <a href="/groups/<%=@user.group.id%>"><%=@user.group.name%></a> .
      </div>
        
    <%end%>
      
  </div>
</div>